        T-Var: {score: i64, test: fn() -> ()} ⊢ score ⇒ i64
        T-Int: {score: i64, test: fn() -> ()} ⊢ 5 ⇒ i64
        Check-Compare: i64 vs i64 => ok (int)
          Unify-Var: i64 ~ i64 => {i64/t3}
      Check-Bool: bool => ok
