        T-Bin-Add: {score: i64, test: fn() -> ()} ⊢ score + 1 ⇒ i64
          T-Var: {score: i64, test: fn() -> ()} ⊢ score ⇒ i64
          T-Int: {score: i64, test: fn() -> ()} ⊢ 1 ⇒ i64
          Unify-Var: i64 ~ i64 => {i64/t4}
